			<div class="content" id="post-content-1486658">
									

<p>An alternative assessment of the alleged 'Destroyers' in <a href="/scp-1050">SCP-1050</a>.</p>
<p>Because I was tired of people automatically assuming they were knockoffs of the <em>Mass Effect</em> universe Reapers. They were not intended as such. While there is evidence to suggest that interpretation, it was my intent to make it possible to hold other views. Headcanon it as you wish, but here's an official alternative.</p>

