														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1486662">
									

<p>I still can't see them as anything but the Mass Effect *Reapers, the whole thing fits them so well (hide out in the 'realm of darkness' aka dark space, they seem to repeat a cycle of destruction, they're space monsters, the tablet can even be seen as a form of the Prothean beacon, etc.)</p>
<p>Nice tale though, it doesn't sway my mind but it's a good read.</p>

